{"word":"Joseph","slug":"joseph","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Joseph</b> <a href=\"#/H3084\">H3084</a><br/><a href=\"#/H3130\">H3130</a> <br/> 1. Son of Jacob:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=30&verse=24'>Gen 30:24</a> <br/> - Personal appearance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=6'>Gen 39:6</a> <br/> - His father's favorite child<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=33&verse=2'>Gen 33:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=4'>Gen 37:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=35'>Gen 37:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=22'>Gen 48:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=5&verse=2'>1Ch 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=4&verse=5'>Joh 4:5</a> <br/> - His father's partiality for, excites the jealousy of his brethren<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=4'>Gen 37:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=11'>Gen 37:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=28'>Gen 37:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=17'>Psa 105:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=9'>Act 7:9</a> <br/> - His prophetic dreams of his fortunes in Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=11'>Gen 37:11</a> <br/> - Sold into Egypt<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=28'>Gen 37:28</a> <br/> - Is falsely reported to his father as killed by wild beasts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=35'>Gen 37:35</a> <br/> - Is bought by Potiphar, an officer of Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=37&verse=36'>Gen 37:36</a> <br/> - Is prospered of God<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=5'>Gen 39:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=21'>Gen 39:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=23'>Gen 39:23</a> <br/> - Is falsely accused, and cast into prison; is delivered by the friendship of another prisoner<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39'>Gen 39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=18'>Psa 105:18</a> <br/> - Is an interpreter of dreams:<br/> b of the two prisoners<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=23'>Gen 40:23</a><br/> b of Pharaoh<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=37'>Gen 41:37</a><br/> - His name is changed to Zaphnath-Paaneah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=45'>Gen 41:45</a> <br/> - Is promoted to authority next to Pharaoh at thirty years of age<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=46'>Gen 41:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=22'>Psa 105:22</a> <br/> - Takes to wife the daughter of the priest of On<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=45'>Gen 41:45</a> <br/> - Provides against the years of famine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=57'>Gen 41:57</a> <br/> - Exports the produce of Egypt to other countries<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=57'>Gen 41:57</a> <br/> - Sells the stores of food to the people of Egypt, exacting of them all their money, flocks and herds, lands and lives<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=47&verse=26'>Gen 47:26</a> <br/> - Exempts the priests from the exactions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=47&verse=22'>Gen 47:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=47&verse=26'>Gen 47:26</a> <br/> - His father sends down into Egypt to buy corn<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=42'>Gen 42</a> <br/> - Reveals himself to his brethren; sends for his father; provides the land of Goshen for his people; and sustains them during the famine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45'>Gen 45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=47&verse=12'>Gen 47:12</a> <br/> - His two sons<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=50'>Gen 41:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=52'>Gen 41:52</a> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=52'>Gen 41:52</a>Ephraim, 1; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=52'>Gen 41:52</a>Manasseh, 1<br/> - Mourns the death of his father<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=14'>Gen 50:14</a> <br/> - Exacts a pledge from his brethren to convey his remains to Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=25'>Gen 50:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=22'>Heb 11:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=19'>Exo 13:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=24&verse=32'>Jos 24:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=7&verse=16'>Act 7:16</a> <br/> - Death of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=26'>Gen 50:26</a> <br/> - His kindness of heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=40&verse=8'>Gen 40:8</a> <br/> - His integrity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=12'>Gen 39:12</a> <br/> - His humility<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=16'>Gen 41:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45&verse=9'>Gen 45:9</a> <br/> - His wisdom<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=57'>Gen 41:57</a> <br/> - His piety<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=52'>Gen 41:52</a> <br/> - His faith<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=45&verse=8'>Gen 45:8</a> <br/> - Was a prophet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=39'>Gen 41:39</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=50&verse=25'>Gen 50:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=19'>Exo 13:19</a> <br/> - God's providence with<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=39&verse=5'>Gen 39:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=22'>Psa 105:22</a> <br/> - His sons conjointly called Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=33&verse=17'>Deu 33:17</a> <br/> - Descendants of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=46&verse=20'>Gen 46:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=37'>Num 26:37</a> <br/> 2. Father of Igal the spy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=13&verse=7'>Num 13:7</a><br/> 3. Of the sons of Asaph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=2'>1Ch 25:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=25&verse=9'>1Ch 25:9</a><br/> 4. A returned exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=42'>Ezr 10:42</a><br/> 5. A priest<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=14'>Neh 12:14</a><br/> 6. Husband of Mary:<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=13&verse=55'>Mat 13:55</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=6&verse=3'>Mar 6:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=25'>Mat 1:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=1&verse=27'>Luk 1:27</a> <br/> - His genealogy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=16'>Mat 1:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=38'>Luk 3:38</a> <br/> - An angel appears and testifies to the innocency of his betrothed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=24'>Mat 1:24</a> <br/> - Dwells at Nazareth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=4'>Luk 2:4</a> <br/> - Belongs to the city of Bethlehem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=4'>Luk 2:4</a> <br/> - Goes to Bethlehem to be enrolled<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=4'>Luk 2:4</a> <br/> - Jesus born to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=25'>Mat 1:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=7'>Luk 2:7</a> <br/> - Presents Jesus in the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=39'>Luk 2:39</a> <br/> - Returns to Nazareth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=39'>Luk 2:39</a> <br/> - Warned in a dream to escape to Egypt in order to save the child's life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=15'>Mat 2:15</a> <br/> - Warned in a dream to return to Nazareth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=23'>Mat 2:23</a> <br/> - Attends the annual feast at Jerusalem with his family<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=51'>Luk 2:51</a> <br/> 7. Of Arimathaea. Begs the body of Jesus for burial in his own tomb<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=60'>Mat 27:60</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=15&verse=47'>Mar 15:47</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=23&verse=56'>Luk 23:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=43&chapter=19&verse=42'>Joh 19:42</a><br/> 8. Three ancestors of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=24'>Luk 3:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=26'>Luk 3:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=30'>Luk 3:30</a><br/> 9. Called Barsabas, surnamed Justus. One of the two persons nominated in place of Judas<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=1&verse=23'>Act 1:23</a><br/> 10. A designation of the ten tribes of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=5&verse=6'>Amo 5:6</a>"}]}